dc_title_s: Cram's township map of Indiana: showing counties, political and congressional townships, base lines, and meridians, all cities, villages, with unabridged index, 3,500 name places, latest federal census
dc_description_s: LR941.; Includes index, description of the township and range and land survey systems, population tables, and inset of Trunk highway. Scale approximately 1:443,520. 7 miles to 1 inch.
